  "title": "Chinese Language Teacher ",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description &amp; Requirements</strong></p>\n<p>our Fiaba Language Center (www.fiabaworld.com) focus on building the foundation of Chinese Language for kids age 7 to 16 through our innovation &amp; unique enrichment programs.</p>\n<p>We welcome you to join us as teacher if you are :</p>\n<p>· Energetic in engaging with young children</p>\n<p>· Passionate in teaching Chinese</p>\n<p>. Patience in guiding children in exam preparation</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Scope</strong></p>\n<p>· Conduct lessons according to our curriculum with cheers and enthusiasm, in ways that motivate active learning, excite curiosity and enrich children knowledge and understanding in Chinese language.</p>\n<p>· Creative and active planning of learning materials and activities.</p>\n<p>· Perform routine care of children to learn in a safe and secure learning environment.</p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<p>· Possess a relevant Chinese Studies Certificate / Diploma / Degree</p>\n<p>· Has accurate pronunciation in speaking Chinese.</p>\n<p>· Able to communicate in English with parents if required.</p>\n<p>· Build rapport with students and parents</p>\n<p>· A team player with a strong sense of responsibility and integrity.</p>\n<p>· Computer literate (MS office – need able to type in Chinese to prepare teaching material)</p>\n<p>. Minimum 2 year of classroom teaching experience</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Job Type:</p>\n<p>Full Time </p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Pls provide detail resume including</p>\n<p>- Photo (a must!)</p>\n<p>- Age</p>\n<p>- Nationality</p>\n<p>- Educational Level</p>\n<p>- Working Experience</p>\n<p>- Email &amp; Contact Number</p>",
